    <text>
        <group>
            <text type="letter" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-01118">
                <body>
                    <opener>
                        <salute rend="inline">
                            <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Никита Иванович!</persName>
                        </salute>
                    </opener>
                    <p>Сегодня две недели, как я из <placeName ref="places.xml#pet01"
                            >Петербурга,</placeName> и хотя я крайне спешу, но ныне сама вижу, что
                        несколько дней более замешкаю на дороге, нежели я надеялась. Я сегодня выеду
                        из <placeName ref="places.xml#per02">Пернау,</placeName> а после завтра
                        приеду в <placeName ref="places.xml#rig01">Ригу</placeName>. <seg
                            xml:lang="fr">Votre Frère se porté bien; il infat demandé hier, si vous
                            étiez envie; faites mes compléments au Grand-Duc; quand je reviendrai à
                            la ville, jè vous dirai des horreurs du <placeName
                                ref="places.xml#bal02">Port Baltique.</placeName>
                        </seg>
                    </p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Екатерина.</persName>
                        </signed>
                        <lb/>
                        <dateline>
                            <placeName ref="places.xml#per02">Пернау.</placeName>
                            <lb/>
                            <date when-custom="1764-07-05">5 число Июля, 1764.</date>
                        </dateline>
                    </closer>
                </body>
            </text>
            <text type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <body>
                    <opener><salute rend="inline"><persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Nikita
                                Ivanovich!</persName></salute></opener>
                    <p>It has been two weeks since I left <placeName ref="places.xml#pet01">St
                            Petersburg</placeName>, and although I am in a great hurry, I
                        now see for myself that I shall be delayed on the road by several days more
                        than I had hoped. Today I am leaving <placeName ref="places.xml#per02"
                            >Pärnu</placeName>, and the day after tomorrow I shall
                        arrive in <placeName ref="places.xml#rig01">Riga</placeName>. <seg
                            xml:lang="fr">Your brother is well; yesterday he asked if you were
                            envious; give my regards to the Grand Duke; when I return to the city, I
                            shall tell you terrible things about the <placeName
                                ref="places.xml#bal02">Baltic Port</placeName>.</seg></p>
                    <closer><signed><persName ref="people.xml#cat01"
                                >Catherine.</persName></signed><lb/><dateline><placeName
                                ref="places.xml#per02">Pärnu.</placeName><lb/><date
                                when-custom="1764-07-05">5 July 1764.</date></dateline></closer>
                </body>
            </text>
        </group>
